<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah berubah.</font>

185
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:48,089
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ji Won berubah pikiran./- Kenapa?</font>

186
00:11:48,089 --> 00:11:50,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu membicarakan kakaknya.</font>

187
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:52,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini fase bulan madumu.</font>

188
00:11:52,069 --> 00:11:54,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Seharusnya dia menggendongmu ke mana-mana.</font>

189
00:11:54,069 --> 00:11:56,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana denganmu? Dia menggendongmu?</font>

190
00:11:58,170 --> 00:11:59,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

191
00:12:03,109 --> 00:12:06,010
<font color=#FFFF00>- Membuatku tidak nyaman./- Apa yang tidak nyaman?</font>

192
00:12:06,010 --> 00:12:09,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu berlebihan. Tidak nyaman.</font>

193
00:12:09,179 --> 00:12:10,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian tidak serasi?</font>

194
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:14,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi bukankah Woo Sung tampan?</font>

195
00:12:17,890 --> 00:12:20,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Woo Sung yang kita kenal?</font>

196
00:12:20,329 --> 00:12:22,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, dia mirip Son Seok Hee.</font>

197
00:12:23,059 --> 00:12:26,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia juga sangat pintar dan manis.</font>

198
00:12:26,329 --> 00:12:29,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Giginya seperti gigi kelinci. Dia tampak seperti ini.</font>

199
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:32,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, kamu terlalu menyukainya.</font>

200
00:12:33,569 --> 00:12:35,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kamu merasa tidak nyaman? Apa masalahnya?</font>

201
00:12:36,339 --> 00:12:39,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah. Aku merasa baik-baik saja sebelum kami bertemu.</font>

202
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:41,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mandi selama dua jam,</font>

203
00:12:41,410 --> 00:12:43,380
<font color=#FFFF00>membersihkan kulit mati, membersihkan wajahku,</font>

204
00:12:43,380 --> 00:12:45,319
<font color=#FFFF00>dan berganti baju 10 kali.</font>

205
00:12:45,319 --> 00:12:47,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga memakai parfum yang sangat wangi.</font>

206
00:12:48,189 --> 00:12:50,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah karena kamu menyukai dia? Karena kamu ingin dia menyukaimu?</font>

207
00:12:51,459 --> 00:12:52,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitukah?</font>

208
00:12:52,929 --> 00:12:56,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi entah kenapa, saat kami bertemu, aku merasa tidak nyaman.</font>

209
00:12:56,859 --> 00:12:58,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Hubungan kami terasa canggung.</font>

210
00:12:58,199 --> 00:13:00,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Perkenalkan dia kepada kami. Kami akan memeriksanya.</font>

211
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:02,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia bersamamu.</font>

212
00:13:02,969 --> 00:13:05,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian akan tahu saat melihat dia?</font>

213
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja. Orang ketiga bisa lebih objektif.</font>

214
00:13:09,309 --> 00:13:12,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik. Kalau begitu, kalian juga harus mengundang seseorang.</font>

215
00:13:13,349 --> 00:13:14,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Minta Ji Won datang.</font>

216
00:13:14,479 --> 00:13:16,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah memberitahumu. Dia menemui kakaknya.</font>

217
00:13:16,319 --> 00:13:19,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar. Young Shim, kamu harus membawa seseorang.</font>

218
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:22,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Membawa siapa? Aku melajang selama 35 tahun tanpa punya gebetan.</font>

219
00:13:22,719 --> 00:13:24,420
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kalau begitu, hubungi ayahmu./- Hei, Kamu!</font>

220
00:13:26,890 --> 00:13:27,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria itu.</font>

221
00:13:28,459 --> 00:13:29,660
<font color=#FFFF00>"Jangan terlambat!"</font>

222
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:33,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak. Kamu salah. "Jangan terlambat!"</font>

223
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:34,900
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seperti ini./- Hubungi pria itu.</font>

224
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:36,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak. Dia membentakku hari ini.</font>

225
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:38,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Krisis menyembunyikan kesempatan!</font>

226
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:44,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku di restoran ayam Jin Jin. Mau mampir ke sini?</font>

227
00:13:48,479 --> 00:13:49,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu di mana?</font>

228
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:08,839
<font color=#FFFF00>"Daftar panggilan terakhir, Ah Reum, Kang Kyung Seok, Jin Jin..."</font>

229
00:14:08,839 --> 00:14:11,339
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kang Kyung Seok"</font>

230
00:14:14,709 --> 00:14:16,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga. Hei!</font>

231
00:14:16,939 --> 00:14:18,309
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kang Kyung Seok"</font>

232
00:14:18,709 --> 00:14:20,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kamu sudah gila? Jangan hubungi dia. Hei!</font>

233
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,650
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ah Reum, jangan. Kumohon jangan./- Ini Kang Kyung Seok.</font>

234
00:14:23,819 --> 00:14:24,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu serius? Pak Kang.</font>

235
00:14:26,689 --> 00:14:28,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Pak Kang.</font>

236
00:14:33,959 --> 00:14:35,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu yakin?</font>

237
00:14:35,929 --> 00:14:39,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus menghubungi Presdir Jang. Dia harus menyusun rencana.</font>

238
00:14:39,130 --> 00:14:40,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak perlu.</font>

239
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:44,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu yakin? Tapi bagaimana kamu bisa membuat dia berubah pikiran?</font>

240
00:14:44,370 --> 00:14:46,309
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dengan hatiku./- Sulit dipercaya.</font>

241
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:49,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada tamu?</font>

242
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Ji Won.</font>

243
00:14:53,410 --> 00:14:56,250
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ji Won?/- Jangan katakan apa-apa kepadanya.</font>

244
00:15:04,689 --> 00:15:05,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa itu saat kamu pulang.</font>

245
00:15:07,089 --> 00:15:08,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

246
00:15:08,429 --> 00:15:10,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampaikan kakak sangat menyukai supnya.</font>

247
00:15:11,729 --> 00:15:12,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

248
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak memikirkan alasan kakak sakit.</font>

249
00:15:19,170 --> 00:15:21,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak pikir karena sup tulang sapi itu.</font>

250
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak sangat bersemangat</font>

251
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:26,280
<font color=#FFFF00>sampai bergegas menghabiskan supnya.</font>

252
00:15:27,109 --> 00:15:28,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti itu sulit bagi kakak.</font>

253
00:15:29,479 --> 00:15:31,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak rasa kakak tidak bisa makan sup tulang sapi lagi.</font>

254
00:15:31,849 --> 00:15:33,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, kakak tidak mau makan itu lagi.</font>

255
00:15:33,719 --> 00:15:35,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak bahkan tidak mau melihatnya.</font>

256
00:15:36,819 --> 00:15:38,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu suka sup tulang sapi, bukan?</font>

257
00:15:42,599 --> 00:15:43,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

258
00:15:44,099 --> 00:15:45,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, kamu bisa makan bagian kakak.</font>

259
00:15:47,969 --> 00:15:50,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, tidak. Kamu akan tetap makan banyak walaupun bukan untuk kakak.</font>

260
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:53,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu sangat menyukai sup tulang sapi.</font>

261
00:15:56,309 --> 00:15:58,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar. Kamu bilang ada yang ingin dibicarakan dengan kakak.</font>

262
00:15:59,449 --> 00:16:00,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak juga sama.</font>

263
00:16:01,209 --> 00:16:02,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Mulai dari kakak? Atau kamu ingin bercerita dahulu?</font>

264
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:05,079
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku akan mulai dahulu./- Baik.</font>

265
00:16:08,790 --> 00:16:09,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku</font>

266
00:16:13,189 --> 00:16:14,829
<font color=#FFFF00>berpacaran dengan Jin Jin.</font>

267
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:19,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia cinta pertamaku.</font>

268
00:16:23,199 --> 00:16:24,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian punya sejarah yang panjang.</font>

269
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:30,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf karena aku tidak memberi tahu Kakak lebih awal.</font>

270
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:36,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang giliran kakak?</font>

271
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

272
00:16:42,219 --> 00:16:45,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak akan berhenti dari "We Got Married" secepatnya.</font>

273
00:16:46,329 --> 00:16:47,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak tidak melakukannya untukmu.</font>

274
00:16:48,229 --> 00:16:50,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak ingin berhenti karena tidak cocok tampil di acara itu.</font>

275
00:16:51,260 --> 00:16:52,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu tidak perlu mengkhawatirkan itu.</font>

276
00:16:53,569 --> 00:16:56,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong-omong, sampai kami mengakhiri acara itu,</font>

277
00:16:56,669 --> 00:16:58,069
<font color=#FFFF00>kalian berdua harus berhati-hati.</font>

278
00:16:58,770 --> 00:17:01,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak dengar ada rumor yang beredar di antara reporter.</font>

279
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:06,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Terakhir,</font>

280
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:09,379
<font color=#FFFF00>ini sangat penting.</font>

281
00:17:10,649 --> 00:17:11,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan.</font>

282
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu mau jjajangmyeon?</font>

283
00:17:17,419 --> 00:17:18,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

284
00:17:20,089 --> 00:17:21,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau porsi besar.</font>

285
00:17:28,069 --> 00:17:30,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang kamu hubungi? Kamu menghubungi Ji Won?</font>

286
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:32,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan khawatir. Dia tidak akan datang.</font>

287
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:36,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berharap setidaknya satu orang akan datang.</font>

288
00:17:37,839 --> 00:17:39,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini membuatku gila.</font>

289
00:17:39,849 --> 00:17:40,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak bisa kupercaya.</font>

290
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:06,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kuduga. Benar.</font>

291
00:18:07,010 --> 00:18:09,040
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku akan membunuhmu./- Kenapa?</font>

292
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Akan kubalas kamu nanti.</font>

293
00:18:10,639 --> 00:18:12,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu tidak tahu batas.</font>

294
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:14,780
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku tidak bisa memercayaimu./- Pak Kang.</font>

295
00:18:16,349 --> 00:18:18,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Ada apa?</font>

296
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:23,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Pak Kang.</font>

297
00:18:23,889 --> 00:18:25,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai.</font>

298
00:18:27,159 --> 00:18:28,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku Kang Kyung Seok.</font>

299
00:18:30,530 --> 00:18:32,329
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hai./- Halo.</font>

300
00:18:32,569 --> 00:18:33,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Bolehkah aku masuk?</font>

301
00:18:46,950 --> 00:18:48,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Mau minum bir?</font>

302
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:51,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengacara Jang dan aku minum terlalu banyak beberapa hari lalu.</font>

303
00:18:51,619 --> 00:18:53,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan minum soda saja.</font>

304
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kamu ke sini?</font>

305
00:18:57,290 --> 00:18:59,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyukai suasananya, bukan minumannya.</font>

306
00:18:59,190 --> 00:19:01,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Young Shim juga begitu.</font>

307
00:19:01,260 --> 00:19:02,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu punya pacar?</font>

308
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

309
00:19:05,099 --> 00:19:06,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan istri?</font>

310
00:19:06,730 --> 00:19:09,139
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku belum menikah./- Young Shim juga belum.</font>

311
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:11,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu tinggal di mana?</font>

312
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:14,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tinggal di Gujeon-dong. 20 menit berjalan kaki dari sini.</font>

313
00:19:14,409 --> 00:19:16,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu juga 20 menit dari rumah Young Shim.</font>

314
00:19:16,510 --> 00:19:17,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa tinggimu?</font>

315
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:19,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurang sedikit dari 180 cm.</font>

316
00:19:19,649 --> 00:19:21,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Sempurna. Selisih tinggi mereka 15 cm.</font>

317
00:19:22,079 --> 00:19:24,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa hobimu? Apa olahraga favoritmu?</font>

318
00:19:24,849 --> 00:19:27,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak berolahraga dan tidak suka berolahraga.</font>

319
00:19:27,450 --> 00:19:29,720
<font color=#FFFF00>- Young Shim juga tidak atletis./- Hei.</font>

320
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:34,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik. Kalian akan saling menatap sebagai langkah terakhir.</font>

321
00:19:34,490 --> 00:19:37,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersiap. Satu, dua, tiga.</font>

322
00:19:46,809 --> 00:19:48,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

323
00:19:54,510 --> 00:19:55,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

324
00:19:57,079 --> 00:19:58,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Reum!</font>

325
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:04,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu datang.</font>

326
00:20:05,559 --> 00:20:06,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf aku terlambat.</font>

327
00:20:07,089 --> 00:20:09,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Jin Jin. Young Shim.</font>

328
00:20:09,399 --> 00:20:11,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Ji Won. Tunggu.</font>

329
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:13,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir kamu Ji Won.</font>

330
00:20:13,730 --> 00:20:15,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo. Senang bertemu denganmu.</font>

331
00:20:17,639 --> 00:20:19,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu rupanya. Dia pacarmu, Young Shim?</font>

332
00:20:19,839 --> 00:20:21,169
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kamu pacarnya?/- Bukan.</font>

333
00:20:21,169 --> 00:20:22,309
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bukan?/- Dia bosku.</font>

334
00:20:22,309 --> 00:20:23,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Bosmu? Baiklah.</font>

335
00:20:29,319 --> 00:20:30,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai jumpa.</font>

336
00:20:30,819 --> 00:20:31,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai jumpa.</font>

337
00:20:31,919 --> 00:20:35,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku dia lebih mirip penyiar.</font>

338
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:36,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa mendadak berkata begitu?</font>

339
00:20:36,559 --> 00:20:38,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku sering mendengar itu.</font>

340
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, bukan?</font>

341
00:20:39,430 --> 00:20:42,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Jin Jin. Itu pasanganmu.</font>

342
00:20:48,669 --> 00:20:51,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Min Ho. Kamu tidak merindukanku?</font>

343
00:20:51,839 --> 00:20:53,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Tampaknya tidak.</font>

344
00:20:53,409 --> 00:20:56,109
<font color=#FFFF00>- Begitukah?/- Kamu datang menjemput Jin Jin?</font>

345
00:20:56,109 --> 00:20:58,379
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tidak. Aku datang untuk uangnya./- Apa?</font>

346
00:20:58,809 --> 00:21:01,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak bilang akan membayarku 100 dolar. Bayar di muka.</font>

347
00:21:01,980 --> 00:21:03,349
<font color=#FFFF00>- Astaga./- Dia sangat materialistis.</font>

348
00:21:03,819 --> 00:21:05,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang untuk uang.</font>

349
00:21:05,349 --> 00:21:06,990
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku akan pulang./- Hati-hati di jalan.</font>

350
00:21:06,990 --> 00:21:08,319
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sampai jumpa./- Selamat malam.</font>

351
00:21:08,319 --> 00:21:09,889
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sampai jumpa./- Jaga dirimu.</font>

352
00:21:09,889 --> 00:21:11,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai jumpa.</font>

353
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,329
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sampai jumpa./- Sampai jumpa.</font>

354
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:21,270
