356
00:21:25,339 --> 00:21:27,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Selalu seperti itu.</font>

357
00:21:29,809 --> 00:21:32,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahun ini, untuk kali pertama</font>

358
00:21:32,849 --> 00:21:34,010
<font color=#FFFF00>dalam sejarah,</font>

359
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:38,480
<font color=#FFFF00>konduktor termuda,</font>

360
00:21:38,919 --> 00:21:42,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Gustavo Dudamel, akan...</font>

361
00:21:42,919 --> 00:21:44,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa jaketku berdebu sekali?</font>

362
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:47,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kenapa kamu melakukan itu? Berhentilah membersihkan jaketmu.</font>

363
00:21:49,129 --> 00:21:50,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, berhenti.</font>

364
00:21:51,129 --> 00:21:53,030
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kenapa?/- Kubilang berhenti.</font>

365
00:21:53,030 --> 00:21:54,169
